          ❓ SixStorm Help Center
        </h1>

        <!-- FAQ 1 -->

        <div
          class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-white/20 text-white"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-400">
            1. Is streaming safe and free?
          </h3>

          <p class="mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300">
            Our platform acts as an aggregator that provides access to publicly
            available streams and information. We do not host any content
            directly on our servers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->

        <div
          class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-white/20 text-white"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-400">
            2. When does live streaming start?
          </h3>

          <p class="mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300">
            Live streaming becomes available when the match begins. Refresh the
            page if the stream does not appear immediately.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->

        <div
          class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-white/20 text-white"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-400">
            3. How can I watch live matches?
          </h3>

          <p class="mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300">
            Simply visit the homepage and access the available stream once the
            match goes live.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->

        <div
          class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-white/20 text-white"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-400">
            4. What tournaments are available?
          </h3>

          <p class="mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300">
            Major cricket tournaments such as international events and league
            matches may be accessible through third-party sources.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 5 -->

